OL,3,COverhaul funding rules to tackle 'dark
OL,4,Cmoney' in politics ` Scottish Greens
OL,6,FPolitical funding rules need to be
OL,7,Foverhauled to tackle the impact of
OL,8,F"dark money", the Scottish Greens have
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe Greens want to see increased
OL,12,Ftransparency and stricter regulation
OL,13,Fon how parties are funded.
OL,15,FThey are calling for new laws to
OL,16,Fensure full disclosure on exactly
OL,17,Fwhere donations to political parties
OL,18,Fcome from.
