OL,3,COverhaul funding rules to tackle 'dark
OL,4,Cmoney' in politics ` Scottish Greens
OL,6,FCurrent rules do not place any limit
OL,7,Fon the size of donations to parties or
OL,8,Findividual politicians.
OL,10,FHowever the regulations require
OL,11,Fdonations to be made from a
OL,12,F"permissible source".
OL,14,FDonations can only be made from
OL,15,Findividuals who are on the UK
OL,16,Felectoral register, while companies
OL,17,Fand organisations such as trade unions
OL,18,Fmust be registered in the UK.
