OL,3,COverhaul funding rules to tackle 'dark
OL,4,Cmoney' in politics ` Scottish Greens
OL,6,FScottish Green co-leader Patrick
OL,7,FHarvie said: "Our politics should
OL,8,Fnever be for sale.
OL,10,F"Yet there is dark money and a cast of
OL,11,Fdodgy donors right at the heart of
OL,12,FWestminster and this election.
OL,14,F"When billionaires buy into political
OL,15,Fparties, they are buying influence.
OL,17,F"The Tory Party has long been a
OL,18,Fvehicle for vested interests and those
OL,19,Fthat benefit from a broken status quo,
OL,20,Fbut Labour are now fast becoming the
OL,21,Fparty of the billionaires.
