OL,3,COverhaul funding rules to tackle 'dark
OL,4,Cmoney' in politics ` Scottish Greens
OL,6,F"In the long-run we need to move to a
OL,7,Ffair system of state funding of
OL,8,Fpolitical parties to create a truly
OL,9,Flevel playing field, but there are
OL,10,Fimportant steps we can take right now.
OL,12,F"We need far stricter limits on
OL,13,Fdonations and campaign spending, and
OL,14,Ftougher transparency and enforcement
OL,15,Frules.
OL,17,F"Our politics needs to represent the
OL,18,Fvoices of normal people and families
OL,19,Facross our country, not the big
OL,20,Fbusinesses and cast of millionaires
OL,21,Fthat are funding our biggest parties.
